OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FThe UK could be heading for a bumper
OL,8,Fbutterfly season ` and even a "painted
OL,9,Flady summer" ` conservationists say as
OL,10,Fthey urge people to join a national
OL,11,Fcount for the insects.
OL,13,FWildlife charity Butterfly
OL,14,FConservation said that a warm, dry
OL,15,Fspring this year has raised hopes that
OL,16,Fbutterflies could be out in force this
OL,17,Fsummer.
OL,26,@pD@_OUqD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
