OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784315921
OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FBut it wants members of the public to
OL,8,Fjoin its annual Big Butterfly Count,
OL,9,Ffrom July 17 to August 9, to help
OL,10,Freveal exactly how butterflies are
OL,11,Ffaring this year.
OL,13,FThe annual citizen science survey
OL,14,Fhelps scientists understand where some
OL,15,Fof the country's most common
OL,16,Fbutterflies and day-flying moths are
OL,17,Fdoing well, struggling or moving
OL,18,Fbecause of climate change and changes
OL,19,Fto habitat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
