PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784315921
OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FButterfly Conservation said heatwaves,
OL,8,Fwarm dry spells and the occasional
OL,9,Fheavy rain have created ideal
OL,10,Fconditions for butterfly breeding and
OL,11,Fcaterpillar growth, with small coppers
OL,12,Fand holly blues already seen in large
OL,13,Fnumbers and peacock, red admiral and
OL,14,Fbrimstones having a promising start to
OL,15,Fthe year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
