PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784315921
OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FExperts at the charity also say there
OL,8,Fare signs of a possible "painted lady
OL,9,Fsummer" ` when the migrant butterfly
OL,10,Farrives in the UK in large numbers `
OL,11,Fbut they need people across the
OL,12,Fcountry to tell them what they are
OL,13,Fseeing to know for sure.
OL,15,FThe hopes for a good summer for the
OL,16,Fwinged insects mark a reversal from
OL,17,Fjust two years ago, when the charity
OL,18,Fdeclared a "butterfly emergency" after
OL,19,Fthe 2024 count delivered the worst
OL,20,Fresults in the scheme's history.
OL,26,@pD@YOUqD@GO]zD@LOUzD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
