PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784315921
OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FA hot, dry, and sunny 2025 boosted the
OL,8,Ffortunes of many species, and this
OL,9,Fyear's spring ` one of the hottest on
OL,10,Frecord ` could prove a boon for
OL,11,Fbutterflies.
OL,13,FBut Butterfly Conservation says that
OL,14,Fis not guaranteed ` and the charity
OL,15,Fwarns it comes against long-term
OL,16,Fdeclines.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
