PN,31606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784315921
OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,FFour fifths (80%) of butterfly species
OL,8,Fhave declined in the past 50 years, as
OL,9,Fa result of habitat loss, pollution
OL,10,Fand climate change, the
OL,11,Fconservationists said.
OL,13,FButterfly Conservation's head of
OL,14,Fengagement, Kate Merry, said: "After
OL,15,Fthe colourful spring with seemingly
OL,16,Flots of beautiful butterflies
OL,17,Fappearing across the UK, it's tempting
OL,18,Fto assume we're heading for a bumper
OL,19,Fsummer, and we'd love nothing more as
OL,20,Fmost of our butterfly species have
OL,21,Fundergone long-term declines.
OL,26,@vD@_OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784315921
OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"But a bright spring is only ever part
OL,8,Fof the story, which is why we need
OL,9,Fpeople out there taking part in the
OL,10,FBig Butterfly Count this summer.
OL,12,F"We genuinely don't yet know how this
OL,13,Fyear will unfold, and the only way to
OL,14,Ffind out is for people to tell us what
OL,15,Fthey're seeing in their own gardens
OL,16,Fand green spaces."
OL,18,FShe added: "Butterflies are icons of
OL,19,Fsummer and, more importantly, key
OL,20,Findicators of the UK's biodiversity
OL,21,Fand environmental health.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@RO]zD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
