PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784315921
OL,3,CBumper butterfly summer? Charity urges
OL,4,Cpeople to join UK-wide count to find
OL,5,Cout
OL,7,F"Every single person that takes part
OL,8,Fin the Big Butterfly Count and submits
OL,9,Ftheir sightings is helping us to see
OL,10,Fhow these pollinators are doing, which
OL,11,Fin turn helps conservationists build a
OL,12,Fwider picture of how all insects are
OL,13,Ffaring."
OL,15,FTo take part in the Big Butterfly
OL,16,FCount, people just need to spend 15
OL,17,Fminutes in any sunny outdoor spot,
OL,18,Fsuch as their garden, park or local
OL,19,Fcountryside, and report their
OL,20,Fsightings.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@HO]
